        <p class="font-heading font-medium text-38 text-blue-900 m-5">Precision</p>
        <p class="paragraph-regular">I pay close attention to my work to reduce the possibility of mistakes, and as a UX designer, I want to make sure the finished product is going to be as perfect as possible.</p>
